  "description": "This dataset comprises local field potential (LFP) recordings from 6-month-old TgF344-AD transgenic rats during linear track locomotion. The TgF344-AD rat model is widely used in Alzheimer's disease research. The recordings provide electrophysiological data suitable for investigating neural activity patterns and oscillatory dynamics in a disease model during naturalistic behavior.",
